      • makeClass

        public org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLClass makeClass(org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLObjectIntersectionOf x)
        given a CE of the form A1 and A2 and ... An, get a class with an IRI formed by concatenating parts of the IRIs of Ai, and create a label assertion, where the label is formed by concatenating label(A1).... note that the reasoner will need to be synchronized after new classes are made Note: modifies ontology but does not flush see materializeClassExpression(..)
